Odoo architecture:
     1.multitenancy 3 tiers Arch:
     2.MVC:
        M(model):postgresql table
        V(view):XML files
        C(Controller):odoo objects
        
 server-ORM (object relational mapper)
 server-web: 1.browser communication 2.WSGI 3. HTTP Queries 4.JSON-RPC
           ->WSGI: WEB SERVER GATEWAY INTERFACE -> for running python web app
           
  (Basic cloud) SaaS--> Software as a Service (Web-based software, on-demand software, on hosted software)
       ---> the way to delivering application over the Internet (no need to installing and maintaing software, access the apps via the Internet
       ---> SaaS apps run on SaaS provider's servers.
       
